Here’s Why you should never accept a travel voucher for a cancelled flight!

✈️ Many vouchers have black out dates and ALL of them expire. 

✈️ Use the cash to book whenever YOU want and with whatever airline you want.

✈️ Plus taking the cash means they have to report the losses to their shareholders, who then force them to make changes to prevent similar losses in the future.
